[{"title":"The Road Not Taken, Robert Frost","url":"/2020/11/23/The%20Road%20Not%20Taken/","content":"<p><code>Two roads diverged in a yellow wood</code><br><code>And sorry I could not travel both</code><br><code>And be one traveler, long I stood </code><br><code>And looked down one as far as I could</code><br><code>To where it bent in the undergrowth</code></p>\n<p><code>Then took the other, as just as fair</code><br><code>And having perhaps the better claim</code><br><code>Because it was grassy and wanted wear</code><br><code>Though as that the passing there</code><br><code>Had worn them really about the same</code></p>\n<p><code>And both that morring equally lay</code><br><code>In leaves no step had trodden black</code><br><code>Oh, I kept the first for another day</code><br><code>Yet konwing how way leads on to way</code><br><code>I doubted if I should over come back</code></p>\n<p><code>I shall be telling this with a sigh</code><br><code>Somewhere ages and ages hence</code><br><code>Two roads dirverged in a wood, and I-</code><br><code>I took the one less traveled by</code><br><code>And that has made all the difference</code></p>\n","categories":["阅读欣赏"],"tags":["read","english"]},{"title":"linux用户管理常用命令","url":"/2020/11/22/linux%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/","content":"<h3 id=\"添加用户：useradd\"><a href=\"#添加用户：useradd\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"添加用户：useradd\"></a>添加用户：useradd</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# tail -5 /etc/passwd</span><br><span class=\"line\">ntp:x:38:38::/etc/ntp:/sbin/nologin</span><br><span class=\"line\">nscd:x:28:28:NSCD Daemon:/:/sbin/nologin</span><br><span class=\"line\">tcpdump:x:72:72::/:/sbin/nologin</span><br><span class=\"line\">admin:x:1000:1000::/home/admin:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql:x:996:994:MySQL server:/var/lib/mysql:/sbin/nologin</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# cat /etc/default/useradd </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> useradd defaults file</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">GROUP=100</span><br><span class=\"line\">HOME=/home</span><br><span class=\"line\">INACTIVE=-1</span><br><span class=\"line\">EXPIRE=</span><br><span class=\"line\">SHELL=/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">SKEL=/etc/skel</span><br><span class=\"line\">CREATE_MAIL_SPOOL=yes</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># -m: Create the user&#x27;s home directory if it does not exist.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># -G: A list of supplementary groups which the user is also a member of.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># it will create a group with the same name as the user.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# useradd -m -G root ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# echo user&#123;01..05&#125; | xargs -n 1 useradd</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# tail -10 /etc/passwd</span><br><span class=\"line\">nscd:x:28:28:NSCD Daemon:/:/sbin/nologin</span><br><span class=\"line\">tcpdump:x:72:72::/:/sbin/nologin</span><br><span class=\"line\">admin:x:1000:1000::/home/admin:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql:x:996:994:MySQL server:/var/lib/mysql:/sbin/nologin</span><br><span class=\"line\">ccying:x:1001:1001::/home/ccying:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:1002::/home/user01:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:1003::/home/user02:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:1004::/home/user03:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:x:1005:1005::/home/user04:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user05:x:1006:1006::/home/user05:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# tail -10 /etc/group</span><br><span class=\"line\">nscd:x:28:</span><br><span class=\"line\">tcpdump:x:72:</span><br><span class=\"line\">admin:x:1000:</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql:x:994:</span><br><span class=\"line\">ccying:x:1001:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:x:1005:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user05:x:1006:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"查看用户信息：finger-id\"><a href=\"#查看用户信息：finger-id\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看用户信息：finger | id\"></a>查看用户信息：finger | id</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># The finger displays information about the system users.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# finger ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">Login: ccying                     Name: </span><br><span class=\"line\">Directory: /home/ccying                 Shell: /bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">Never logged in.</span><br><span class=\"line\">No mail.</span><br><span class=\"line\">No Plan.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># Print user and group information for the specified USER, or (when USER omitted) for the current user.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# id ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">uid=1001(ccying) gid=1001(ccying) groups=1001(ccying),0(root)</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"查看当前登录的用户名：whoami\"><a href=\"#查看当前登录的用户名：whoami\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看当前登录的用户名：whoami\"></a>查看当前登录的用户名：whoami</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# whoami</span><br><span class=\"line\">root</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"切换用户：su\"><a href=\"#切换用户：su\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"切换用户：su\"></a>切换用户：su</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# whoami</span><br><span class=\"line\">root</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# pwd</span><br><span class=\"line\">/root</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# su - ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login: Sun Nov 22 14:17:40 CST 2020 on pts/0</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[ccying@ccying ~]$ whoami</span><br><span class=\"line\">ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">[ccying@ccying ~]$ pwd</span><br><span class=\"line\">/home/ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[ccying@ccying ~]$ su -</span><br><span class=\"line\">Password: </span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login: Sun Nov 22 14:17:58 CST 2020 on pts/0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"删除用户：userdel\"><a href=\"#删除用户：userdel\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除用户：userdel\"></a>删除用户：userdel</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# grep user /etc/passwd</span><br><span class=\"line\">tss:x:59:59:Account used by the trousers package to sandbox the tcsd daemon:/dev/null:/sbin/nologin</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:1002::/home/user01:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:1003::/home/user02:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:1004::/home/user03:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:x:1005:1005::/home/user04:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user05:x:1006:1006::/home/user05:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# ls /home</span><br><span class=\"line\">admin  ccying  user01  user02  user03  user04  user05</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># -r: Files in the user&#x27;s home directory will be removed along with the home directory itself and the user&#x27;s mail spool.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# userdel -r user05</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# grep user /etc/passwd</span><br><span class=\"line\">tss:x:59:59:Account used by the trousers package to sandbox the tcsd daemon:/dev/null:/sbin/nologin</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:1002::/home/user01:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:1003::/home/user02:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:1004::/home/user03:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:x:1005:1005::/home/user04:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# grep user /etc/group</span><br><span class=\"line\">users:x:100:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:x:1005:</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# ls /home</span><br><span class=\"line\">admin  ccying  user01  user02  user03  user04</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"新建用户组：groupadd\"><a href=\"#新建用户组：groupadd\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新建用户组：groupadd\"></a>新建用户组：groupadd</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# tail -5 /etc/group</span><br><span class=\"line\">ccying:x:1001:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:x:1005:</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># -p: use this encrypted password for the new group</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# groupadd -p 123456 user</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# tail -5 /etc/group</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:x:1005:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user:x:1006:</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# tail -5 /etc/gshadow</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:!::</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:!::</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:!::</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:!::</span><br><span class=\"line\">user:123456::</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"修改用户信息：chfn-usermod\"><a href=\"#修改用户信息：chfn-usermod\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改用户信息：chfn | usermod\"></a>修改用户信息：chfn | usermod</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# finger ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">Login: ccying                     Name: </span><br><span class=\"line\">Directory: /home/ccying                 Shell: /bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login Sun Nov 22 14:21 (CST) on pts/0</span><br><span class=\"line\">No mail.</span><br><span class=\"line\">No Plan.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># chfn  is used to change your finger information.  This information is stored in the /etc/passwd file, and is displayed by the finger program.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# chfn ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">Changing finger information for ccying.</span><br><span class=\"line\">Name []: ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">Office []: </span><br><span class=\"line\">Office Phone []: </span><br><span class=\"line\">Home Phone []: (0000)5751-134</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Finger information changed.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# finger ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">Login: ccying                     Name: ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">Directory: /home/ccying                 Shell: /bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">Office: (0000)5751-134</span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login Sun Nov 22 14:21 (CST) on pts/0</span><br><span class=\"line\">No mail.</span><br><span class=\"line\">No Plan.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# grep ccying /etc/passwd</span><br><span class=\"line\">ccying:x:1001:1001:ccying,,,(0000)5751-134:/home/ccying:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# grep user /etc/passwd</span><br><span class=\"line\">tss:x:59:59:Account used by the trousers package to sandbox the tcsd daemon:/dev/null:/sbin/nologin</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:1002::/home/user01:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:1003::/home/user02:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:1004::/home/user03:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:x:1005:1005::/home/user04:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# finger user04</span><br><span class=\"line\">Login: user04                     Name: </span><br><span class=\"line\">Directory: /home/user04                 Shell: /bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login Sun Nov 22 16:13 (CST) on pts/3</span><br><span class=\"line\">No mail.</span><br><span class=\"line\">No Plan.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># -l: The name of the user will be changed from LOGIN to NEW_LOGIN.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># -d: The user&#x27;s new login directory.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># -s: The name of the user&#x27;s new login shell.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# usermod -l _user04 -d /home/_user04 -s /usr/bin/sh user04</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# grep user /etc/passwd</span><br><span class=\"line\">tss:x:59:59:Account used by the trousers package to sandbox the tcsd daemon:/dev/null:/sbin/nologin</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:1002::/home/user01:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:1003::/home/user02:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:1004::/home/user03:/bin/bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">_user04:x:1005:1005::/home/_user04:/usr/bin/sh</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# finger _user04</span><br><span class=\"line\">Login: _user04                    Name: </span><br><span class=\"line\">Directory: /home/_user04                Shell: /usr/bin/sh</span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login Sun Nov 22 16:13 (CST) on pts/3</span><br><span class=\"line\">No mail.</span><br><span class=\"line\">No Plan.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# id _user04</span><br><span class=\"line\">uid=1005(_user04) gid=1005(user04) groups=1005(user04)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# su - _user04</span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login: Sun Nov 22 16:13:48 CST 2020 on pts/3</span><br><span class=\"line\">su: warning: cannot change directory to /home/_user04: No such file or directory</span><br><span class=\"line\">-sh-4.2$ exit</span><br><span class=\"line\">logout</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# tail -5 /etc/group</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:x:1005:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user:x:1006:</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># -G: A list of supplementary groups which the user is also a member of. </span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# usermod -G user user01</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# usermod -G user user02</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# usermod -G user user03</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# tail -5 /etc/group</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:x:1005:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user:x:1006:user01,user02,user03</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"删除用户组：groupdel\"><a href=\"#删除用户组：groupdel\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除用户组：groupdel\"></a>删除用户组：groupdel</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# tail -5 /etc/group</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:x:1005:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user:x:1006:user01,user02,user03</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# groupdel user</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# tail -5 /etc/group</span><br><span class=\"line\">ccying:x:1001:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:x:1002:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:x:1003:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:x:1004:</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:x:1005:</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# id user01</span><br><span class=\"line\">uid=1002(user01) gid=1002(user01) groups=1002(user01)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# tail -5 /etc/gshadow</span><br><span class=\"line\">ccying:!::</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:!::</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:!::</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:!::</span><br><span class=\"line\">user04:!::</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"修改用户密码：passwd\"><a href=\"#修改用户密码：passwd\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改用户密码：passwd\"></a>修改用户密码：passwd</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# echo &quot;ccying&quot; | passwd --stdin ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">Changing password for user ccying.</span><br><span class=\"line\">passwd: all authentication tokens updated successfully.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# su - user01</span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login: Sun Nov 22 16:40:49 CST 2020 on pts/3</span><br><span class=\"line\">[user01@ccying ~]$ su - ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">Password: </span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login: Sun Nov 22 16:40:58 CST 2020 on pts/3</span><br><span class=\"line\">[ccying@ccying ~]$ su -</span><br><span class=\"line\">Password: </span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login: Sun Nov 22 16:41:26 CST 2020 on pts/3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"批量修改用户密码：chpasswd\"><a href=\"#批量修改用户密码：chpasswd\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"批量修改用户密码：chpasswd\"></a>批量修改用户密码：chpasswd</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# grep user /etc/shadow</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:!!:18588:0:99999:7:::</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:!!:18588:0:99999:7:::</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:!!:18588:0:99999:7:::</span><br><span class=\"line\">_user04:!!:18588:0:99999:7:::</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# echo user&#123;01..03&#125;:$((RANDOM+100000000)) | tr &quot; &quot; &quot;\\n&quot; &gt; ./user_password.txt</span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# cat ./user_password.txt </span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:100005026</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:100012230</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:100015865</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# chpasswd &lt; user_password.txt </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# su - ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login: Sun Nov 22 16:42:29 CST 2020 on pts/3</span><br><span class=\"line\">Last failed login: Sun Nov 22 16:50:58 CST 2020 on pts/3</span><br><span class=\"line\">There was 1 failed login attempt since the last successful login.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[ccying@ccying ~]$ su - user01</span><br><span class=\"line\">Password: </span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login: Sun Nov 22 16:42:16 CST 2020 on pts/3</span><br><span class=\"line\">[user01@ccying ~]$ su -</span><br><span class=\"line\">Password: </span><br><span class=\"line\">Last login: Sun Nov 22 16:51:07 CST 2020 on pts/3</span><br><span class=\"line\">Last failed login: Sun Nov 22 16:56:48 CST 2020 on pts/3</span><br><span class=\"line\">There was 1 failed login attempt since the last successful login.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# grep user /etc/shadow</span><br><span class=\"line\">user01:$6$bFzQy/j.mwjMx1Yz$IGqtCIchkxBzZ3rg.I.D/bApUpd0zOwap5lD.A8aA3LWRJTneQBOpfKIe8wbWk7dov12WUMnsyEMvwF1rgmsK0:18588:0:99999:7:::</span><br><span class=\"line\">user02:$6$5NpDK/uRwUX/zEej$5fxb6Xaw3ySOQ8CEwm68BDXa1JPbYAXkjUqwvNWKfkd2UIWoA7XAZ0cl9Mm.H.I/20mJC1dd15sj4pVYZRRgC0:18588:0:99999:7:::</span><br><span class=\"line\">user03:$6$v.Rte/NbxRST$pu1ZpuDvaNQOCWvMExlkicZT5Ju47RJHFMP8LfQcdcaUS33DT8kDyD.MHWCgBNLSTLXcWuf8qhFoK3jyD35Uv.:18588:0:99999:7:::</span><br><span class=\"line\">_user04:!!:18588:0:99999:7:::</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"修改用户密码有效期：chage\"><a href=\"#修改用户密码有效期：chage\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改用户密码有效期：chage\"></a>修改用户密码有效期：chage</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# chage -l ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">Last password change                    : Nov 22, 2020</span><br><span class=\"line\">Password expires                    : never</span><br><span class=\"line\">Password inactive                    : never</span><br><span class=\"line\">Account expires                        : never</span><br><span class=\"line\">Minimum number of days between password change        : 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">Maximum number of days between password change        : 99999</span><br><span class=\"line\">Number of days of warning before password expires    : 7</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># -M: Set the maximum number of days during which a password is valid.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># -W: Set the number of days of warning before a password change is required.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># -I: Set the number of days of inactivity after a password has expired before the account is locked.</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# chage -M 60 -W 14 -I 3 ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# chage -l ccying</span><br><span class=\"line\">Last password change                    : Nov 22, 2020</span><br><span class=\"line\">Password expires                    : Jan 21, 2021</span><br><span class=\"line\">Password inactive                    : Jan 24, 2021</span><br><span class=\"line\">Account expires                        : never</span><br><span class=\"line\">Minimum number of days between password change        : 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">Maximum number of days between password change        : 60</span><br><span class=\"line\">Number of days of warning before password expires    : 14</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"显示已登录用户信息：w-who\"><a href=\"#显示已登录用户信息：w-who\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"显示已登录用户信息：w | who\"></a>显示已登录用户信息：w | who</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# w</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 17:33:56 up 20:53,  3 users,  load average: 0.01, 0.04, 0.05</span><br><span class=\"line\">USER     TTY      FROM             LOGIN@   IDLE   JCPU   PCPU WHAT</span><br><span class=\"line\">root     pts/0    14.25.56.97      14:17    1:58m  0.13s  0.10s -bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">root     pts/1    14.25.56.97      17:33    4.00s  0.00s  0.00s -bash</span><br><span class=\"line\">root     pts/3    14.25.56.97      16:06    4.00s  0.23s  0.00s w</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# who -a -H</span><br><span class=\"line\">NAME       LINE         TIME             IDLE          PID COMMENT  EXIT</span><br><span class=\"line\">           system boot  2020-11-22 04:40</span><br><span class=\"line\">LOGIN      tty1         2020-11-21 20:40               511 id=tty1</span><br><span class=\"line\">LOGIN      ttyS0        2020-11-21 20:40               510 id=tyS0</span><br><span class=\"line\">           run-level 3  2020-11-21 20:40</span><br><span class=\"line\">root     + pts/0        2020-11-22 14:17 02:00        7815 (14.25.56.97)</span><br><span class=\"line\">root     + pts/1        2020-11-22 17:33 00:01        9672 (14.25.56.97)</span><br><span class=\"line\">           pts/2        2020-11-22 16:17              8610 id=ts/2  term=0 exit=0</span><br><span class=\"line\">root     + pts/3        2020-11-22 16:06   .          8653 (14.25.56.97)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"显示用户执行命令历史记录：history\"><a href=\"#显示用户执行命令历史记录：history\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"显示用户执行命令历史记录：history\"></a>显示用户执行命令历史记录：history</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@ccying ~]# history 3</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 1007  less /var/log/lastlog</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 1008  man history</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 1009  history 3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","categories":["学习记录"],"tags":["linux"]},{"title":"旭日","url":"/2020/11/22/%E6%97%AD%E6%97%A5/","content":"<img src=\"/2020/11/22/%E6%97%AD%E6%97%A5/%E6%97%AD%E6%97%A5.jpg\" class=\"\" title=\"旭日\">","categories":["生活趣事"],"tags":["life"]}]